data.description: Aspire at Sun Valley offers affordable new homes for sale in Coalinga, CA. Choose from 3 spacious designs with up to 4 bedrooms and live a relaxed lifestyle close to downtown and great schools. Enjoy the convenience of having Hwy 33 & 198 within close proximity. Offered By: K. Hovnanian CA Land Holdings, LLC The Primrose offers: Open living space perfect for entertaining. Spacious designer kitchen with large pantry and island. Luxurious owner's suite with huge walk-in closet. Loft for playing, studying or use as media room. Convenient 3-car garage for additional vehicle or workshop.
